title: The latest in US-Cuba talks with Jorge Ponce | Opinion - Conservative
text:
(Before It's News)
Guest: Jorge Ponce, Cuban American writer and columnist, joins me for a look at the latest from Cuba……….there are reports that Cuba will be sending troops to Syria to assist Assad, a move that can not please the US………also we will look at the growing repression in Cuba and other developments in US-Cuba relations……………..
